{
  "stem": "268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How would I describe--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With neighbors.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very-- also coal miners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, the union was called brotherhood, but it also spilled over to the spouses and to the children and family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were very close-knit families.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all coal miners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother would visit with them, they would visit in our house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes I remember dad, when I go to sleep, he would get-- he would get irritated because some neighbor would come in and yak and yak and tell us stories about [COUGHS] her husband and about domestic stories, you know, complaining.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mom used to always listen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because she had such a sympathetic ear for everyone, most people would sit around-- this is before TV, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they would come in and sip some tea or coffee and talk about the domestic problem.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mom would listen, like a confessional, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the neighbors-- we had a very close relation, of course, and I played with their kids, as well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So our neighbors were very, very friendly, and we had common grounds of interest because, again, families of coal miners share the same interest, with the exception of, you know, obviously I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when it comes to, you know-- except on Sundays or Shabbats, we would part ways.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But other than that, we had common interest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was a very-- very congenial, very, I must say, friendly atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these were tenement houses owned by the mines, by the coal mines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very modern houses for [BACKGROUND NOISE] Polish because this was German territory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Germany, as you know, was much more developed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Their buildings were more modern, westernized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Water was inside water.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
